{
  "stem": "25651.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That meant lemon tea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And of course, half an hour later, I needed to go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I had girls' trousers, you see, so I was afraid to tell the publican that I had girls' trousers, that I needed to go to the toilet where I could sit down.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because in Czechoslovakia, if a boy needed to go, you just went around the corner, and you just did it in nature.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I couldn't do it in nature.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I had to go to the proper toilet.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it wasn't like here where you go to the flush toilet.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I sort of sat there in agony, what seemed, now, like hours, till they came.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I was happy enough when they came, and I still didn't go to the toilet until we got home.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But because of the shame of wearing these girls' trousers, I refused to go and play with this girl.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I had actually not seen her since.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I never-- I wrote her about this story.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She doesn't remember this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it's very amusing, but it's very, you know, it's sort of formative in, in my, in my own thing that I-- this was the first girlfriend that I threw over.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The next main event was-- well, we went periodically to Poland.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The next main event was-- I was going to tell you-- going to this Maccabi Hatzair camp, because it was in Zilina in-- in Slovakia, which in those days was a day's journey by train.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was sent alone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there were other benyamin.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Benyamin means the youngest, you know, like Benjamin was the youngest tribe.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Six.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the hut was in the mountains above Zilina.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Very long walk, very tiring climb.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
